rows.label: qst101808_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, Possah! It's been a while!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0002
rows.name:
Vahsah!
And...oh no, not you again.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0003
rows.name: What? This...really Jizo?

rows.label: qst101808_msg0004
rows.name: That me.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0005
rows.name:
Hmmm...
Hmmmmmmmm...
Hmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmmm...

rows.label: qst101808_msg0006
rows.name:
Vahsah.
You still remember Possah?

rows.label: qst101808_msg0007
rows.name:
Would I forget the girl my Driver
has a crush on?

rows.label: qst101808_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Meh-meh?! Why Vahsah letting
cat out of bag?!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0009
rows.name:
Jizo not roundy-fatty, fluffy-puffy
anymore...

rows.label: qst101808_msg0010
rows.name:
But still Jizo! Oh, Jizo!
Welcome back!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0011
rows.name: Jizo happy to be back with Possah!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0012
rows.name:
Guess we got ourselves
a happy ending.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0013
rows.name:
Jizo would have come back faster.
But Vahsah get in big trouble with
massive debt.

rows.label: qst101808_msg0014
rows.name:
Vahsah... Getting poor little Jizo in
deep trouble again?

rows.label: qst101808_msg0015
rows.name:
Well, everything fine now. Cleaned up
Vahsah's silly mistake!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0016
rows.name:
Thank you, friends!
For all of many helps!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0017
rows.name:
Not even know how to express
deep gratitude...

rows.label: qst101808_msg0018
rows.name:
Jizo and Vahsah and Possah all
happy now! Jizo want friends to
be all happy too!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0019
rows.name:
After little bit of shampoo, Jizo all
nice and fluffy-puffy again!

rows.label: qst101808_msg0020
rows.name:
Yes...Jizo should spruce up.
Nice to see friends!
